data.description: Wow!  Check out this beautifully remodeled ranch on the south side of Hillsboro.  Updated/remodeled from top to bottom.  Updates include:  Heated tile floors throughout the main level, solid wood doors, light fixtures, main level trim.  Newer appliances, newer shingles, newer siding.  Updated kitchen w/a new sink & new microwave.  Remodeled bathrooms with tile showers.  Potential 4th bedroom in basement, just needs an egress window!  Wet bar w/small fridge.  Large strorage/utility room.  Oversized and heated garage w/large work bench.  Large stamped concrete patio in a big backyard.  Large shed.  Huge 37ft X 15ft gravel parking pad.
